  "detailed_description": "Throughout his life, Joseph Teddie has been dead set on one singular goal: Uncover the depths of Melody Memorial. Why? He doesn't know. All he knows is that he needs to.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/804230/extras/6ced65580520ac3a541f3d71077df96f.avif?t=1745594519\" width=283 height=398 /></span><br>In this musical adventure game, Joseph will travel and sing through creepy caverns, mischievous marshes, and even a casino to get to the legendary locale. But for the first time since he was a little kid, he won't be alone. After an encounter with local celebrity Angeli Lovely, she decides to piggyback on his journey in hopes of digging up the rumored treasure of Melody Memorial.<br><br>Are you ready to believe?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet charming and quirky characters! </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore places to solve puzzles!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sing along to the rhythm!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Laughs and emotions aplenty!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Set high scores in Arcade mode!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Featuring an original soundtrack by Alexander Lyons and artwork by Alice Tan!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/804230/extras/7bc63f65d8bc86088d13298ddc201ca6.avif?t=1745594519\" width=478 height=292 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Throughout his life, Joseph Teddie has been dead set on one singular goal: Uncover the depths of Melody Memorial. Why? He doesn't know. All he knows is that he needs to.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/804230/extras/6ced65580520ac3a541f3d71077df96f.avif?t=1745594519\" width=283 height=398 /></span><br>In this musical adventure game, Joseph will travel and sing through creepy caverns, mischievous marshes, and even a casino to get to the legendary locale. But for the first time since he was a little kid, he won't be alone. After an encounter with local celebrity Angeli Lovely, she decides to piggyback on his journey in hopes of digging up the rumored treasure of Melody Memorial.<br><br>Are you ready to believe?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet charming and quirky characters! </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore places to solve puzzles!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sing along to the rhythm!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Laughs and emotions aplenty!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Set high scores in Arcade mode!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Featuring an original soundtrack by Alexander Lyons and artwork by Alice Tan!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/804230/extras/7bc63f65d8bc86088d13298ddc201ca6.avif?t=1745594519\" width=478 height=292 /></span>",
